You don't need to overthink it.

512
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:56,119
If anything happens to me,
the secret must not be lost.

513
00:41:57,079 --> 00:41:58,280
You will be safe.

514
00:41:58,280 --> 00:42:00,239
Tan Xian told me the secret in this way.

515
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:05,239
